渤海新闻网）唐山市披露货车司机服用农药死亡事件调查情况"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "255 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453856406"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI1YqGr+qPm8VDEAMaCDYzMTM2NjA4IOfQxIMGMA84sgNAFHIJNDUzODU2NDA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1618049255.306813", "card_id": "Q_453083089", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 93}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多不懂电脑的小白也买联想拯救者？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a6ed1630f943d5fa1cbec9e24d845ef_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "242 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453083089"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1YqGr+qPm8VDEAMaCDYyOTY0ODA0INmmrIMGMAo45QFAFXIJNDUzMDgzMDg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1618049255.3071141", "card_id": "Q_453676197", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 108}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "陕科大与西安工大「因地铁站命名掐架，幼儿遭殃」，地铁站命名对高校是否有这么重要？为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "西安地铁 14 号线一站点被命名为「西安工业大学站」，引发邻居陕西科技大学不满——距离远近差不多，凭什么不用自己的校名。 「斗法」中陕科大出了「奇招」，令旗下幼儿园劝退西安工业大学教职工子女 40 名。 此新闻一曝出，两所高校，无一赢家，都贴上了不清爽、不大气的标签。高校掐架、幼儿遭殃。拿幼儿园小朋友撒气，官僚中带着幼稚，偏狭中又有刻薄，本是教书育人的圣地，涵养正气的净土，这么做，的确是有辱斯文、贻笑大方。 央视网评 | 站台名比不上好声名"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a9cd5952f35748214a683a9fc1ea2a41_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "230 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453676197"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1YqGr+qPm8VDEAMaCDYzMDk2NjEzIKP8voMGMAU4uwJAFnIJNDUzNjc2MTk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1618049255.3076496", "ca